snippet.title: ΔV: Rings of Saturn - Tales from the Rings - Trailer
snippet.description:
⟹ Get Free DLC here ⟹ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1211880?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=talestrailer
⟹ Or here ⟹ https://www.gog.com/pl/game/dv_rings_of_saturn_tales_from_the_rings

You can download a Free DLC "Tales from the Rings" with supplemental material set in the universe of ΔV: Rings of Saturn, including:

- Free E-book "Howling at the Stars".
- A digital artbook.
- Desktop wallpapers.
- Avatar images.
- Cellphone wallpapers and ringtones.
- Creator asset pack: ship 3d models and full-resolution crew portraits you can use in your own fan arts.
- Ship paint templates you can use to customize your ships.
★ Seamless animations for streaming and desktop background.
